| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1649 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 68c8c896-aaf2-5d02-b2f6-979e50f03c21"
